trans-unit.source: Contains a read-only collection of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone"></xref> controls.
trans-unit.target: Innehåller en skrivskyddad samling <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone"> </xref> kontroller.

trans-unit.source: The WebPartZoneCollection class contains the collection of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone> controls that exist on a Web Parts page.
trans-unit.target: Klassen WebPartZoneCollection innehåller samlingen av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>kontroller som finns på en sida med webbdelar.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>

trans-unit.source: It is used primarily by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control to track and manage all the zones.
trans-unit.target: Det används främst av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>kontrollen att spåra och hantera alla zoner.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control keeps a reference to the collection of zones on a page in its read-only <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.Zones%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>behåller kontrollen en referens till samlingen av zoner på en sida i dess skrivskyddad <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.Zones%2A>egenskap.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.Zones%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: The WebPartZoneCollection class is useful when you want to carry out operations on multiple zones or their contents at the same time, or when you need to locate a particular zone and examine or change its contents.
trans-unit.target: Klassen WebPartZoneCollection är användbar när du vill utföra åtgärder på flera zoner eller innehållet på samma gång, eller när du vill söka efter en viss zon och granskar eller ändrar dess innehåll.

trans-unit.source: Although the collection of zones itself is read-only and you cannot change the size of the collection object itself, you can still get references to the individual zones within the collection, and when you have a reference to an individual zone object, you can change its property values.
trans-unit.target: Även om insamling av zoner själva är skrivskyddad och du kan inte ändra storleken på samlingsobjektet, du kan fortfarande få referenser till enskilda zoner i samlingen när du har en referens till en zon för enskilda objekt, kan du ändra dess egenskapsvärden.

trans-unit.source: The WebPartZoneCollection class has two constructors.
trans-unit.target: Klassen WebPartZoneCollection har två konstruktorer.

trans-unit.source: The first one, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection.%23ctor>, simply initializes an empty instance of a new WebPartZoneCollection.
trans-unit.target: Det första <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection.%23ctor>, initierar en tom instans av en ny WebPartZoneCollection.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection.%23ctor>

trans-unit.source: The second one, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection.%23ctor%28System.Collections.ICollection%29>, initializes a collection by passing in an existing collection of zones.
trans-unit.target: Det andra <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection.%23ctor%28System.Collections.ICollection%29>, initierar en samling genom att passera i en befintlig samling av zoner.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection.%23ctor%28System.Collections.ICollection%29>

trans-unit.source: The WebPartZoneCollection class contains an <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection.Item%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Klassen WebPartZoneCollection innehåller en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection.Item%2A>egenskap.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection.Item%2A>

trans-unit.source: This property allows you to locate a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone> control within the collection by passing in a string identifier.
trans-unit.target: Den här egenskapen kan du söka efter en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>kontroll i samlingen genom att passera i en strängidentifierare.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>

trans-unit.source: The zone is located by matching the string identifier to the value of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ID%2A> property on a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase> zone.
trans-unit.target: Zonen finns genom att matcha strängidentifierare till värdet för den <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ID%2A>egenskapen för en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase>zon.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase> </xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ID%2A>

trans-unit.source: The WebPartZoneCollection class also has several methods that are useful for examining or accessing its contents.
trans-unit.target: WebPartZoneCollection-klassen har också flera metoder som är användbara för att undersöka eller få åtkomst till innehållet.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection.Contains%2A> method determines whether a particular zone exists in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection.Contains%2A>metoden avgör om en viss zon finns i samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection.Contains%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection.CopyTo%2A> method copies the collection to an array of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase> objects.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection.CopyTo%2A>metoden kopierar samlingen till en matris med <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase>objekt.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection.CopyTo%2A>

trans-unit.source: Finally, the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection.IndexOf%2A> method returns the index of a particular zone within the collection.
trans-unit.target: Slutligen den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection.IndexOf%2A>metoden returnerar index för en viss zon i samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection.IndexOf%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes an empty instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en tom instans av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control uses this constructor within its own constructor to initialize a new instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection> class for a Web Parts page.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>kontrollen använder den här konstruktorn i sin egen konstruktorn för att initiera en ny instans av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection>klass för en sida med webbdelar.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: Initializes an instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection"></xref> class by passing in a collection of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en instans av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection"> </xref> klassen genom att passera i en samling <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone"> </xref> objekt.

trans-unit.source: Use the WebPartZoneCollection constructor when you want to create a custom collection of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone> objects to carry out programmatic operations on them.
trans-unit.target: Använd konstruktorn WebPartZoneCollection när du vill skapa en anpassad samling med <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>objekt som ska utföra programmässiga åtgärder på dem.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>

trans-unit.source: For example, you could access the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.Zones%2A> property and create a subset of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone> objects on a Web Parts page, assigning them to a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection> object, and then carry out operations on the child controls or various properties of only that subset of zones.
trans-unit.target: Du kan till exempel komma åt den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.Zones%2A>egenskapen och skapa en deluppsättning av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>objekt på en sida med webbdelar, tilldela dem till en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection>objektet och sedan utföra åtgärder på underordnade kontroller eller olika egenskaper för endast den del av zoner.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.Zones%2A>

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Collections.ICollection> of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Collections.ICollection>av <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone"> </xref> objekt.</xref:System.Collections.ICollection>

trans-unit.source: The collection of zones is <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Insamling av zoner är <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: One of the objects in the collection is <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref> or is not of type <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Ett objekt i samlingen är <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref> eller är inte av typen <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Returns a value indicating whether a particular zone exists in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Returnerar ett värde som anger om en viss zon finns i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: The Contains method enables you to check a particular <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone> object and determine whether it is in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection> collection.
trans-unit.target: Metoden innehåller kan du kontrollera en viss <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>objekt och avgöra om den är i ett <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection>samling.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone"></xref> that is checked to determine whether it is in the collection.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone"> </xref> som kontrolleras för att avgöra om den är i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: A Boolean value that indicates whether a particular zone is in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Ett booleskt värde som anger om en viss zon finns i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Copies the collection to an array of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Kopierar samlingen till en matris med <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase"> </xref> objekt.

trans-unit.source: The CopyTo method is useful when you want to create a custom array that can contain the zones in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection> collection, a subset of those zones, or a superset of those zones.
trans-unit.target: Metoden CopyTo är användbart när du vill skapa en anpassad matris som kan innehålla zonerna i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection>samling, en delmängd av dessa zoner eller en supermängd zonerna.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase"></xref> array to contain the copied collection.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase"> </xref> matris som innehåller den kopierade samlingen.

trans-unit.source: The starting point in the array at which to place the collection contents.
trans-unit.target: Startpunkten i matrisen som du vill placera innehållet samling.

trans-unit.source: Returns the position of a particular member of the collection.
trans-unit.target: Returnerar positionen för en viss medlem i mängden.

trans-unit.source: The IndexOf method is useful if you have multiple <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone> zones on a Web Parts page, and you need to know the ordinal position of one zone relative to the other zones.
trans-unit.target: IndexOf-metoden är användbar om du har flera <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>zoner på en sida med webbdelar, och du behöver veta ordningstalspositionen för en zon i förhållande till andra zonerna.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase"></xref> that is a member of the collection.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase"> </xref> som är medlem i mängden.

trans-unit.source: An integer that indicates the position of a particular object in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Ett heltal som anger positionen för ett visst objekt i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Returns a specific member of the collection by passing in an integer.
trans-unit.target: Returnerar en viss medlem i samlingen genom att passera i ett heltal.

trans-unit.source: The Item property enables you to access a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone> object within a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection> collection by using an index number that represents its ordinal position in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen Item kan du få en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>objekt inom en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection>samlingen med hjälp av ett index som representerar dess ordningstal i samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>

trans-unit.source: The index number for a particular <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone"></xref> within a collection.
trans-unit.target: Antalet index för en viss <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone"> </xref> i en samling.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone"></xref> at the specified index in the collection.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone"> </xref> med det angivna indexet i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Returns a specific member of the collection by passing in a unique identifier.
trans-unit.target: Returnerar en viss medlem i samlingen genom att passera i en unik identifierare.

trans-unit.source: The Item property enables you to access a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone> object within a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection> collection by using a string identifier for a particular zone.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen Item kan du få en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>objekt inom en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection>med hjälp av ett sträng-ID för en viss zon.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>

trans-unit.source: All matching on string identifiers is case-insensitive.
trans-unit.target: Alla matchning på strängidentifierare är skiftlägeskänsliga.

trans-unit.source: The unique identifier for a particular <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone"></xref> within the collection.
trans-unit.target: Den unika identifieraren för en viss <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone"> </xref> i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: The first in the collection whose ID equals the value of id.
trans-unit.target: Först i samlingen med ID lika med värdet för id .
